title: G3 Mid main LF Jungle duo pref
body:
Hi Guys,

I'm a mech engineer LF a mature duo for after work hours/weekends to climb to plat->diamond. I've been playing since s4 but only on/off and usually stop at gold. Main Akali/Talon. Can play other roles but definitely pref mid. I'm down to duo with any other main role but obviously jungle is better.

Let me know!
